author: Russell Brand
description:
Fauci’s old phone has finally been found—and investigators want to know if he lied. But the real story is bigger: Australia just admitted the COVID vaccine causes more harm than good for young people, and RFK Jr. is pulling it from the CDC schedule too. So why were we told it was safe and effective—by Fauci, by Obama, by nearly every establishment voice? In this episode, I go deep into what they knew, when they knew it, and why they pushed so hard. From global reversals to vaccine warnings to institutional rot, the truth is finally cracking through the surface. Are we ready to face it?
